Package: UCSCTrackTools
Version: 1.0.1
Title: Tools to convert BAM files to BigWig and to create session track line
Author: Chao-Jen Wong
Maintainer: Chao-Jen Wong <cwon2@fhcrc.org>
Depends:  R (>= 3.2.2)
Imports: RColorBrewer, biovizBase, GenomicAlignments, Rsamtools, BiocParallel, rtracklayer, GenomeInfoDb
Description: Tools to convert BAM files to bigWig files using coverage on genome positions.
  The session track line append the track lines for each bigWig file. Note that the bigWig
  files have to saved in /home/tapscott/ucsc/bigWig directory. The url portal is
  "http://tapscott:FSHD@xfiles.fhcrc.org:7007/ucsc/tapscott/bigWig"
License: Artistic-2.0
LazyLoad: yes

